title: 2011 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 27 of 27)
description:
2011 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC (...SO FAR)

Over the past two months, I've been gathering, and torrenting all of my Christian Music released at some point during this past year.  Each torrent contained several albums.  There were 26 torrents in total, for a count of 674 Christian Albums.  Today's 27th torrent contains 21 more albums, bringing the total count up to 695 Christian Albums...
